DESCRIPTION:Kiana Lodge Easter Buffet & Egg Hunt Sun April 5th\, 2026 Brunc
	h Buffet 11:00AM - 02:00PM\,Easter Bunny & Egg Hunt 12:00PM Come visit wit
	h the Easter bunny and enjoy a tasty Easter brunch at Kiana Lodge. Kids ar
	e encouraged to bring their own basket so they can find the hidden eggs fi
	lled with goodies! Adults: $54.60\, Children 5-12: $21.84\, 5 and Under: $
	5.46 Beverages: Cash Bar with Mimosa & Bloody Mary Specials Highchairs ava
	ilable in limited quantity please email info@kianalodge.com to reserve. Al
	l Children must be accompanied by an adult\, please provide your own baske
	t for the egg hunt. Menu: Fresh Sliced Seasonal Fruit Assorted Breakfast P
	astries Scrambled Eggs Crisp Bacon Savory Sausage Links Sliced Glazed Ham 
	Cedar Ridge Potatoes Spam Fried Rice Croissant French Toast Mixed Green Sa
	lad with balsamic dressing Kiana Signature Salmon Chef Carved Prime Rib wi
	th Creamy Horseradish & Au Jus Teriyaki Chicken Steamed Rice Seasonal Roas
	ted Vegetables Omelet Station Dessert Buffet\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.c
	om/events/#/details/kiana-easter-brunch-egg-hunt/18252393/2026-04-05T00\n\
	nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/kiana-easter-brunch-egg-h
	unt/18252393/2026-04-05T00
LOCATION:Kiana Lodge\, 14976 Sandy Hook Rd NE\, Poulsbo\, WA
